        "text_j4QPiT": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Everyone on an LBT trip likes riding for hours at a time, being outdoors all day and night, and socializing on bikes and in camp. Riders have been all ages, races and genders. If you're interested in that, then Lichen Bike Tours is right for you!</p><p>Shorter trips usually have a few first-timers. Are you new to bike tours with camping? You might be:</p><ol><li>A cyclist who wants to do more camping </li><li>A camper who wants to do more cycling</li><li>New to both</li></ol><p> </p>"
          }
        },
