            "heading": "Rentals",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_NrjEVP": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Our riders often use their own bicycle, bags, and camping equipment. To reflect this, our trip prices are low, but not too low. </p><p>LBT offers equipment rentals and connects you with a local bike shop that can fit you for a bike rental. Equipment rentals include assistance during the trip and a pre-trip packing session so that we are assured that you have the necessary equipment, it fits on your bike and doesn't interfere with your comfort while riding. </p><h3>Advice</h3><p>If you are very new to doing a camping trip on your bike and you feel like you want some help before you take a trip, then book time with Lichen Bike Tours to receive personalized advice, a list of specific equipment recommendations, and a lot of encouragement. These sessions are discounted when purchased with a trip. </p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
